Stop at the luxurious Salieri Theatre Restaurant for a tantalizing pre-show meal consisting of succulent appetizers and specially crafted main courses, and then skip over to nearby Lyceum Theatre for an equally rich, visual feast. These dinner and show packages offer unbeatable value for an evening of unparalleled entertainment.
